===Awards===

* [[Fishbein Trophy]] (1) 1961
* [[Herman Trophy]] (1) 1962
* Blackwood Award 2005 <ref>[http://www.fpabridge.org/blackwood.htm Foundation for the Preservation and Advancement of Bridge Blackwood Award]</ref>

